#define GREETINGS ["How delicious, a morsel wanders into the pit. Begone, %s, before I decide you’d look better as ash.","Your soul smells like rot and wasted potential, %s. Flee my sight, or I shall feast.","A fragile thing, truly. Does the stench of sulfur frighten you yet, %s? It should.","I have no taste for such pathetic offerings. Crawl away, %s, while you still have legs to carry you.","You are not worthy of my shadow, let alone my time. Fade, %s.","Tremble, little creature. The abyss is watching, and it finds you... amusingly insignificant, %s.","Do you hear the whispers, %s? They are hungry for a life as fleeting as yours.","You dance on the precipice of oblivion. Tell me, %s, does the fall terrify you?","I shall let you live a while longer, %s. Despair makes the eventual end so much sweeter.","Your life is but a candle in a hurricane. Let me blow it out, %s.","You have a desperate kind of courage, %s. It will make your eventual demise all the more exquisite.","Step lightly, %s. These lands are stained with blood you could never hope to spill.","I have seen empires crumble; do you honestly believe you are a threat, %s?","Your essence is flickering, %s. I could snap your thread with a single thought.","I find your persistence... irritating. Cease your meddling, %s.","Welcome to the inferno, %s. I wonder how long your spirit will remain untainted here.","You possess a jagged soul. I might enjoy watching it shatter, %s.","I have tracked your path through the void, %s. It leads only to my doorstep.","You have a darkness in you, %s. It is the only thing that makes you tolerable.","Do not be deceived by my hospitality. The abyss has no mercy, %s.","A soul of substance. Tell me, %s, would you like to see what lies beyond the veil?","Your power is... pungent. It radiates like a fresh wound. I find it tempting, %s.","Many have sought to challenge me, %s. All of them now reside beneath my boots.","You are an interesting mutation of reality. Let us see how much of you