#define WrestleWin ["How delicious, a morsel wanders into the pit. Begone, %s, before I decide you’d look better as ash." ,"Your soul smells like rot and wasted potential, %s. Flee my sight, or I shall feast." ,"A fragile thing, truly. Does the stench of sulfur frighten you yet, %s? It should." ,"I have no taste for such pathetic offerings. Crawl away, %s, while you still have legs to carry you." ,"You are not worthy of my shadow, let alone my time. Fade, %s." ,"Tremble, little creature. The abyss is watching, and it finds you... amusingly insignificant, %s." ,"Do you hear the whispers, %s? They are hungry for a life as fleeting as yours." ,"You dance on the precipice of oblivion. Tell me, %s, does the fall terrify you?" ,"I shall let you live a while longer, %s. Despair makes the eventual end so much sweeter." ,"Your life is but a candle in a hurricane. Let me blow it out, %s." ,"You have a desperate kind of courage, %s. It will make your eventual demise all the more exquisite." ,"Step lightly, %s. These lands are stained with blood you could never hope to spill." ,"I have seen empires crumble; do you honestly believe you are a threat, %s?" ,"Your essence is flickering, %s. I could snap your thread with a single thought." ,"I find your persistence... irritating. Cease your meddling, %s." ,"Welcome to the inferno, %s. I wonder how long your spirit will remain untainted here." ,"You possess a jagged soul. I might enjoy watching it shatter, %s." ,"I have tracked your path through the void, %s. It leads only to my doorstep." ,"You have a darkness in you, %s. It is the only thing that makes you tolerable." ,"Do not be deceived by my hospitality. The abyss has no mercy, %s." ,"A soul of substance. Tell me, %s, would you like to see what lies beyond the veil?" ,"Your power is... pungent. It radiates like a fresh wound. I find it tempting, %s." ,"Many have sought to challenge me, %s. All of them now reside beneath my boots." ,"You are an interesting mutation of reality. Let us see how much of you is truth, %s." ,"Welcome, traveler. Your strength is a rare vintage. Let us see if it tastes as good as it looks, %s." ,"Your defiance warms the cold chambers of my heart, %s. It is... intoxicating." ,"You are a storm in the dark. I have missed such chaotic beauty, %s." ,"If you intend to bleed, %s, do it somewhere else. I only want your power." ,"We are cut from the same wretched cloth, %s. Join me, and we shall rewrite this reality." ,"Your strength is a beacon for the damned. Tell me, %s, are you ready to become a monster?" ,"At last, an equal. My dark throne has been dreadfully empty, %s." ,"You radiate a power that tears at the seams of this world. I am... aroused by your potential, %s." ,"I have waited eons for a force like you to challenge the natural order. Let us begin our dance, %s." ,"Your presence consumes the very light around you. It is glorious, %s. Let us drown the world in it." ,"A god among worms. You and I, %s... we shall bring the apocalypse to their doorsteps." ]

#define WrestleDefeat ["A nuisance! I grow bored of this game, %s. Enjoy your fleeting victory." ,"How... unexpected. This world is far more chaotic than I anticipated, %s." ,"You have only delayed the inevitable, %s. My patience is eternal." ,"I should have vanished you into the shadows when you first appeared, %s." ,"Go on, celebrate. It won't save you when I truly decide to end you, %s." ,"A fluke of fate! You will not be so fortunate the next time we cross paths, %s." ,"I am unaccustomed to such insolence, %s. You have earned my ire." ,"Perhaps I underestimated your lack of self-preservation, %s." ,"My power remains unbent, %s. Your victory is nothing but a shadow." ,"You have played your hand, %s. Ensure it was worth the cost." ,"You have disrupted the natural flow, %s. I find that... remarkably tedious." ,"Do you think you have mastered the dark, %s? You haven't even begun to understand it." ,"A momentary lapse in focus. I shall remember your insolence, %s." ,"This battle was a trivial distraction, %s. It ends now." ,"I have no more use for this sector. Keep your hollow victory, %s." ,"You are more persistent than you appear, %s. A pity that persistence will lead to your doom." ,"I am withdrawing, %s. Not out of defeat, but out of absolute disinterest in your petty struggle." ,"You have bested me today, %s. But the abyss always takes what is owed." ,"Very well, %s. We shall see if you can handle the consequences of your victory." ,"I find this current outcome... unacceptable. I shall rectify it." ,"You fight with a darkness that nearly rivals mine, %s. I am... intrigued." ,"I yield this territory to you for now, %s. Enjoy the silence before the storm." ,"Your victory is an interesting variable, %s. I shall incorporate it into my calculations." ,"I grow tired of these games, %s. Next time, there will be no mercy." ,"You are a fascinating deviation, %s. Let us see how long you survive." ,"You have matched my ferocity, %s. A rare achievement for a soul such as yours." ,"I have been bested. A rare occurrence, and one I do not intend to repeat, %s." ,"This battle has left me... curious. Let us see where your path leads, %s." ,"You have earned my respect, for whatever that is worth in this dying world, %s." ,"I shall retreat to the shadows to mend my strength. Do not get comfortable, %s." ,"Finally, a worthy adversary! You have truly earned your seat in the apocalypse, %s." ,"I concede the victory, %s. But be warned: a force such as yours will soon call to the deepest darkness." ,"You possess a power that challenges my own. This is a day that will be etched in history, %s." ,"You have proven yourself a titan. Let us see if you can hold that ground when the world ends, %s." ,"Truly remarkable. I look forward to our next encounter, %s. Do try to survive until then."]
